commit.message: messed with new task, added deletion for tasks, screwed around with the time allocation thingy
added conversion formula from duration to chunk number in allocateTime
formatted global variables to be ready to import from Task
added error message if not enough time is available
Started work on forms for task entry

Added indication of logged in user, and filtering out stuff of other users
Also fixed gitignore by removing and readding everything
added login, logout, and email confirmation functionality
Added view, at localhost:8000/cal/ which shows all the stuff in the database
Makes it so certain fields can be NULL/blank

Added CALAPP, which is the app holding the calendar
added all the models required for calendar
and they work with the default admin page
Edited README file as a test
